but I don't want to think about it.

1008
01:14:57,469 --> 01:14:59,266
It's all too sad and...

1009
01:15:00,402 --> 01:15:02,666
- I'm a beautician.
- Really?

1010
01:15:02,968 --> 01:15:04,663
Yes. Shall I do your make-up?

1011
