1200
01:29:56,834 --> 01:30:01,293
- Why? What's happened?
- Nothing. I just want to leave.

1201
01:30:01,400 --> 01:30:04,460
- What about Africa?
- What would I do there?

1202
01:30:04,600 --> 01:30:06,363
So where will you go?

1203
01:30:07,234 --> 01:30:08,865
I don't know.

1204
01:30:09,266 --> 01:30:13,965
Come to my house. I'm alone,
and I owe you both so much.

1205
01:30:14,067 --> 01:30:15,534
- Really?
- Really.

1206
01:30:15,633 --> 01:30:17,726
- For a few days?
- Forever.

1207
01:30:17,834 --> 01:30:21,167
- Great! What about you?
- I don't know.

1208
01:30:21,300 --> 01:30:23,666
