I will come to get you.

1228
01:31:32,001 --> 01:31:33,764
I've nothing more to say.

1229
01:31:35,001 --> 01:31:36,195
Let's go!

1230
01:31:49,400 --> 01:31:52,233
Thank you for everything.

1231
01:31:52,333 --> 01:31:54,324
I'll never forget tonight.

1232
01:31:56,834 --> 01:31:58,961
Let's go to bed.

1233
01:31:59,066 --> 01:32:01,660
It's been a very busy day.

1234
01:32:01,767 --> 01:32:05,533
We'll discuss things tomorrow.
Have you seen Yolanda?

1235
01:32:05,633 --> 01:32:07,726
She went to her room.

1236
01:32:07,867 --> 01:32:12,201
- Sister Rat? Sister Snake?
- Sister Rat is with the Marquise.

1237
01:32:12,300 --> 01:32:15,030
Sister Snake is confessing.

1238
01:32:16,166 --> 01:32:17,166
Come.

1239
01:32:20,500 --> 01:32:22,365
Leave that.

1240
01:32:22,467 --> 01:32:25,265
- Leave it.
- It's such a mess.

1241
01:32:25,367 --> 01:32:27,358
You're impossible!

1242
01:32:44,166 --> 01:32:46,532
I got used to sewing with you...

1243
01:32:47,800 --> 01:32:50,268
to taking communion with you...

1244
01:32:50,367 --> 01:32:52,767
to worrying about you.

1245
01:32:53,166 --> 01:32:55,760
I hate the thought of being separated.

1246
01:32:56,867 --> 01:32:58,494
That isn't a sin.

1247
01:32:59,433 --> 01:33:02,628
God is love.
He made us to love.

1248
01:33:06,100 --> 01:33:07,658
I love you too.

1249
01:33:08,500 --> 01:33:11,560
I learned to sew
to spend more time with you.

1250
01:33:12,933 --> 01:33:16,458
- To be closer to you.
- But it's impossible!

1251
01:33:16,567 --> 01:33:20,230
I'm a nun and you're a priest.

1252
01:33:21,333 --> 01:33:22,732
We made our vows.

1253
01:33:22,834 --> 01:33:26,429
- Why are you afraid?
- I don't know, Father.

1254
01:33:28,899 --> 01:33:31,599
Sister Damned, what are you doing with
the tiger in church?

1255
01:33:31,899 --> 01:33:33,730
I'm going to Albacete.

1256
01:33:34,400 --> 01:33:37,233
Will you take care of him?

1257
01:33:37,333 --> 01:33:38,994
I'll miss him so much but...

1258
01:33:39,100 --> 01:33:43,093
I can't take him with me.

1259
01:33:43,667 --> 01:33:46,659
He knows you two.

1260
01:33:46,800 --> 01:33:51,768
You're going to be a family.
He'll have a home.

1261
01:33:52,033 --> 01:33:54,593
Everyone knew but me.

1262
01:33:56,633 --> 01:33:58,567
Even you, Boy.

1263
01:33:59,767 --> 01:34:01,564
Our love is like you.

1264
01:34:01,667 --> 01:34:05,694
A tiger that grew unnoticed
within these walls.

1265
01:34:05,800 --> 01:34:09,634
We'll love you like a son,
and you'll never go hungry.

1266
01:34:09,734 --> 01:34:12,960
- I promise.
- Well, I'm going.

1267
01:34:13,734 --> 01:34:17,261
And you'd better behave yourself.

1268
01:34:20,933 --> 01:34:22,366
God bless you.

1269
01:34:50,400 --> 01:34:52,459
Yolanda, it's me. Let me in.

1270
01:34:58,899 --> 01:35:04,233
I'm going to Thailand tomorrow.
I want to say good-bye.

1271
01:35:04,333 --> 01:35:06,392
We have lots to talk about.

1272
01:35:11,200 --> 01:35:12,997
Let me in!

